title: Toys Sound Pack
description: Toys Sound Effects Bundle brings the ambience of the Toy Story-like sound effects to you.
longDescription: Toys Sound Effects Bundle brings the ambience of the Toy Story-like sound effects to you. Toys Sound Effects Bundle includes these sound effects; plastic and wooden toy sounds, stones, button sounds, various instruments such as shakers, bells, and xylophone sounds, and so on! With this bundle, you can capture the atmosphere of Toy Story and can make projects like this. With “Toys Sound Effects Bundle” you have access to toy sound effects, instrument sound effects, bell sound effects, horn sound effects, and designed sound effects that you need for your project. Toys Bundle will help with all your playful and cheerful sound effects needs. With this bundle, you may be able to create the atmosphere that you desire for your project!
technicalDetails:
Features:

Number of Audio Waves: 210+

Number of Audio Cues: 210+

Sample rate / bit rate: 24bit – 96kHz

Do Sound FX loop: no

Minutes of audio provided: 15 min 3 sec

Supported Development Platforms:

Windows: Yes

Mac: Yes
